
<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 238, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8">
        <p>For the past few years I have been going to UVU to pursue a Biotechnology degree. While going to school I took some programming courses, and I fell in love with programming.</p>

