<p>I have built some really awesome programs using Ruby on Rails, HTML, CSS, Typescript, Javascript, and I am currently building an app using React, Apollo, and GraphQL.

Currently I am working full time as a freelance developer building out websites for clients, but I am also looking for a more stable work environment.</p>

          <button
